### =============================================================================
### RAIS-API - OAI-PMH 2.0 con CERIF JSON (PeruCRIS)
### Pruebas de los 6 verbos OAI-PMH y 7 sets PeruCRIS
### Registros seleccionados con datos mas completos segun directrices PeruCRIS
### =============================================================================

### =============================================================================
### 1. IDENTIFY - Informacion del repositorio
### =============================================================================

### Identify - Obtener informacion del repositorio
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=Identify

### =============================================================================
### 2. LIST METADATA FORMATS - Formatos de metadatos soportados
### =============================================================================

### ListMetadataFormats - Sin identificador (todos los formatos)
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListMetadataFormats

### =============================================================================
### 3. LIST SETS - Conjuntos disponibles
### =============================================================================

### ListSets - Obtener todos los sets disponibles
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListSets

### =============================================================================
### 4. LIST IDENTIFIERS - Listado de identificadores por set
### =============================================================================

### --- PERSONS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListIdentifiers&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=persons

### --- ORGUNITS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListIdentifiers&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=orgunits

### --- PUBLICATIONS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListIdentifiers&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=publications

### --- PROJECTS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListIdentifiers&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=projects

### --- FUNDINGS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListIdentifiers&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=fundings

### --- EQUIPMENTS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListIdentifiers&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=equipments

### --- PATENTS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListIdentifiers&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=patents

### =============================================================================
### 5. LIST RECORDS - Registros completos con metadatos CERIF
### =============================================================================

### --- PERSONS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=persons

### --- ORGUNITS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=orgunits

### --- PUBLICATIONS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=publications

### --- PROJECTS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=projects

### --- FUNDINGS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=fundings

### --- EQUIPMENTS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=equipments

### --- PATENTS ---
GET http://localhost:3000/oai?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=perucris-cerif&set=patents

